Measurements
(in mm; 
10 males
, 
8 females
). Body length: male 20.9–24.7 (22.7); female 22.3–24.0 (28.5). Fore wing length: male 25.5–28.7 (26.9); female 28.3–31.2 (29.4). Fore wing width: male 9.2–10.6 (9.8); female 9.7–11.3 (10.5). Head width: male 6.0–7.0 (6.6); female 6.6–7.1 (6.9). Pronotum width: male 5.9–7.7 (6.9); female 6.4–8.0 (7.5). Abdomen width: male 6.1–7.2 (6.5); female 6.4–7.5 (7.0). Ovipositor length: female 6.0–8.4 (7.7).
